# Agent memory files
# CLAUDE.md is a shared project guide and is tracked with the root live docs.
AGENTS.md

# docs/ work notes — local-only (plans/specs/reviews/completion reports)
# All future docs/ additions stay local too. Already-tracked files are
# unaffected by .gitignore. Re-include docs/protocol/ so the protocol
# source-of-truth can still be added/updated; project docs (install/
# release/signing) remain tracked as already-committed.
/docs/*
!/docs/protocol/

# Local-only handoff/exec-plan clutter (untracked; files kept on disk).
# Precise paths — do NOT ignore the whole handoffs/ or .exec-plan/ trees,
# since both contain tracked files (older handoffs, committed plan states).
handoffs/handoff-20260702-1511.md
handoffs/handoff-20260702-1839.md
